Rhoen-Klinikum Says German Customs Probing Wages at Suppliers

-- B y   T o m   L a v e l l
-- 
2011-09-23T14:43:38Z

-- http://www.bloomberg.com/news/2011-09-23/rhoen-klinikum-says-german-customs-probing-wages-at-suppliers.html
Rhoen-Klinikum AG (RHK)  said German
customs officers visited a number of its facilities this week in
a months-old probe of collective wage agreements at service
providers at the company’s hospitals.  Rhoen-Klinikum is giving authorities its full cooperation
and is “convinced of having acted at all times in accordance
with the law,” the company said today in a statement on its
website.  To contact the editor responsible for this story:
Tom Lavell at 
 tlavell@bloomberg.net  